name: MAGIC PLANET 02/30
description:
The night sky is a wonder to behold, by which I mean something I  wonder about!
8 trillion planets in Milky way galaxy and 2 trillion galaxy! Is not crazy? 
Often inspiring me to wonder, what is my place in all of this?

I always close my eyes, dream up colorful planets in mysterious space and when I open my eyes they materialize in front of me, see!

2/30
